author: dicka
msg: Backing out recent changes, as they broke the compilation of all the automated tests.  In addition they would prevent customers from compiling clients stubs (and probably also server skeletons) due to dependency from include/ files to src/ files, which are not available to the customer.

IMessageData.hpp must not be dependent on anything that is outside the include/axis tree.  Is there an alternative, or do we need to seperate out a portion of the included file, such that it is suitable to be kept within the include/axis tree.
